    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83c\udf1f Pristine & Perfect \u2013 A Mint Condition Gem That's Ready to Impress! \ud83c\udf1f\n\nRare opportunity alert! This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition \u2014 and we mean it! Every inch of this car reflects exceptional care and quality. The exterior is flawless, the interior is spotless, and everything runs and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. This isn't your average used car \u2014 it's a like-new experience at a used-car price. Whether you're a first-time buyer wanting the best start or a savvy driver who refuses to compromise on quality, this is the one. Come see it for yourself \u2014 we're confident it will exceed your expectations! \ud83d\ude97\u2728",
      "price": 46000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and full transparency is a priority. The exterior shows considerable wear \u2014 multiple scratches, several dents, and paint fading or chipping in various areas. The interior has seen heavy use, with worn seating, staining, and general deterioration of surfaces. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will likely require attention; it is best suited for a buyer comfortable with repairs or looking for a project vehicle. This is an honest, as-is sale, and we encourage any interested buyer to inspect the vehicle thoroughly before purchasing.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition, and we want to be completely transparent with prospective buyers about what that means. The exterior shows significant wear throughout, including multiple dents, scratches, and areas of paint fading or chipping that are clearly visible. The body panels show signs of age and rough use, and there may be minor rust in certain areas. Mechanically, the car runs but has known issues that will require attention \u2014 buyers should budget for repairs and should not expect a trouble-free experience without some investment. The interior reflects the same level of wear, with worn upholstery, scuffs on trim pieces, and general signs of heavy use over the years. This listing is priced accordingly to reflect the car's true state, and we strongly recommend a pre-purchase inspection so you know exactly what you're getting. This vehicle is best suited for a mechanically inclined buyer, someone looking for a project car, or a buyer who needs basic transportation and is comfortable with its limitations.",
      "price": 7000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed honestly as a fair-condition car suitable for everyday reliable transportation. The exterior shows visible wear, including minor dents, light scratches, and areas where the paint has faded or chipped over time. There may be some surface rust in spots, though nothing structurally compromising. The interior is functional but shows signs of use \u2014 expect worn upholstery, minor scuffs, and general aging. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though a buyer should anticipate some maintenance needs in the near future, such as routine servicing or minor repairs. This is a solid choice for someone seeking dependable transportation at an honest price, without expecting a showroom-ready vehicle.",
      "price": 15500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
